claude_meter
============

This package is vendored (copied) into wio-claude-buddy so the host bridge is
self-contained. It originates from the author's own "claude-usage" meter project
and provides the ~/.claude transcript parsing and plan-usage math
(scanner / pricing / aggregator / limits / snapshot) that
host/buddy_ble_bridge.py builds on.

